OL,3,CBoy, 14, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after stabbing
OL,6,FA teenager has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder after a
OL,8,Fsuspected stabbing in Cirencester.
OL,10,FPolice say they were called to a house
OL,11,Fon Upper Churnside shortly after 11am
OL,12,Fon Sunday 15 March where they found a
OL,13,Fteenage girl and adult man had
OL,14,Fsuffered minor injuries.
OL,16,FA 14-year-old boy from Wiltshire was
OL,17,Fsubsequently arrested on suspicion of
OL,18,Fattempted murder.
