OL,3,CBoy, 14, arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cattempted murder after stabbing
OL,6,FOfficers from Gloucestershire Police
OL,7,Fare now asking for anyone with
OL,8,Finformation to come forward.
OL,10,FOfficers say they want to hear from
OL,11,Fanyone who lives in the surrounding
OL,12,Farea who has CCTV or doorbell footage
OL,13,Ffrom either before or after the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FAnyone with information or footage is
OL,17,Fasked to provide this to police online
OL,18,Fquoting incident 153 of 15 March.
